### TEST IDENTITY SWAP GATEWAY
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/token-swap
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firebaseIdToken": "{{firebaseToken}}"
}

### FETCH DASHBOARD COUNTERS
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/metrics
X-E2E-ID: {{e2eId}}
X-Session-ID: {{sessionId}}

### LOG OPERATIONAL EXPENSE
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions/expense
X-E2E-ID: {{e2eId}}
X-Session-ID: {{sessionId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 250.00,
  "description": "Drop Wire 50m Patch for Block A Repair",
  "expenseCategory": "WIRE"
}

### LOG WHOLESALE ISP VENDOR SETTLEMENT
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions/isp-settlement
X-E2E-ID: {{e2eId}}
X-Session-ID: {{sessionId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionTypeName": "AP Fiber",
  "amountPaid": 3500.00,
  "paymentStatus": "FULL_PAYMENT",
  "settlementNotes": "Cleared balance statement for June loop"
}

### AGGREGATE TRI-LEDGER CASH SUMMARY
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/daily-summary?targetDate=2026-06-07
X-E2E-ID: {{e2eId}}
X-Session-ID: {{sessionId}}

### SEARCH CUSTOMER LOOKUPS
GET {{baseUrl}}/customers/search?name=Satish&block=Block A
X-E2E-ID: {{e2eId}}
X-Session-ID: {{sessionId}}
